Not only delicious but beautiful, as well. It looks like a big, clear, wiggly ruby! The celery gives a nice crunch to the usual mushiness of cranberry sauce. And I love the hair dryer suggestion...the hot towel becomes cold in seconds and takes too long. This recipe has a permanent place on our Thanksgiving menu.

