Rating: 4
It's a great compromise! Everyone loved it last Thanksgiving and now it's a tradition. It's also very simple to make. I recommend using real 100% cranberry juice, not the cocktail. Also, we had a small group last year so I cut the recipe in half and chilled it in a simple plastic bowl. It didn't look as beautiful as a mold, but it tasted great.

